As an urban business district in France, offices of various atmospheric pressures are located. The harmony between nature and buildings is impressive.

Very pleasant water fountain to admire. Bordered by skyscrapers, we have a beautiful view of the arch on one side, and the triumphal arch in the distance on the other side. The shopping center being next door, there are several shops nearby.

Office district, with splendid skyscrapers and well-kept gardens, a successful mix, a contemporary atmosphere, walking from the arch of defense you can admire fountains and works of art, it's a free open-air museum!

La Fontaine is located in the middle of the Esplanade de la D√©fense, crossing the territories of Courbevoie and Puteaux, on the route of the historical axis. The work consists of a rectangular basin of 57 m by 26, covered with enamel of different colors. The pool empties at one end through a drain, forming a waterfall. It is powered by 66 autonomous water jets, each illuminated by its own spotlights.

Beautiful, large fountain in the most modern neighborhood of Paris.  This work by Israeli artist Yaacov Agam responds to the monumental scale of the site. It measures 26 x 86 meters and has a 72-meter spillway, made of mosaic manufactured in Venice. A wonder that combines water, light and sound to obtain a wonderful result.
